1. How to change the domain name of the wordpress
- In the dashboard, got to setting-general to change the url
- Change the domain name of the server
- Point the domain to the server

2. How to increase the configuation of wordpress
- https://premium.wpmudev.org/blog/increase-memory-limit/
- make the change recursive
suPHP_ConfigPath /home/username/public_html

3. How redirect the page if it is mobile device.
 <script type="text/javascript">

if (screen.width <= 699) {
document.location = "mobile.html";
}

.htaccess
# BEGIN WordPress
<IfModule mod_rewrite.c>
RewriteEngine On
RewriteBase /
RewriteRule ^index\.php$ - [L]
RewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME} !-f
RewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME} !-d
RewriteRule . /index.php [L]
</IfModule>
suPHP_ConfigPath /home/satday5/public_html
# END WordPress


How to change the domain name:
1. change the site link in wordpress
2. Change the new domain's A record
3. Change the nameserver
4. Change the primary domain in inmotion hosting

